<title>around the world in twelve days</title>
<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/Voyeurism/~3/eGIh-BK_vuk/around-the-world-in-twelve-days.html</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">http://voyager.blogs.com/voyeurism/2012/05/around-the-world-in-twelve-days.html</guid>
<description>Phileas Fogg and Passepartout made the journey in eighty days. by God's grace alone, over the next twelve days, i'm about to fulfill the same lifelong dream :-) 17 May SQ16 SIN -&gt; SFO 20 May UA500 SFO -&gt; Phoenix,...</description>
<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Phileas Fogg and Passepartout made the journey in eighty days.</p>
<p>by God's grace alone, over the next twelve days, i'm about to fulfill the same lifelong dream :-)</p>
<p>17 May SQ16 SIN -&gt; SFO</p>
<p>20 May UA500 SFO -&gt; Phoenix, Arizona (PHX)</p>
<p>22 May UA1635 PHX -&gt; EWR</p>
<p>23 May UA117 EWR -&gt; HKG (arrive HKG 24 May)</p>
<p>25 May Dragonair KA854 HKG -&gt; Wuhan, China (WUH)</p>
<p>(26 May; panelist at a seminar on '<a href="http://www.whiceb.com/symposium.html">Virtuality as a Frontier for Management Information Systems research</a>')</p>
<p>27 May China Southern CZ3543 WUH -&gt; Shanghai Pudong (PVG)</p>
<p>28 May SQ825 PVG -&gt; SIN<br /></p>
<p>catch me if you can :-)</p>
