<item>
<title>the Six Learnings Project - extended funding approved</title>
<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/Voyeurism/~3/5sUe9O1_cxE/the-six-learnings-project-extended-funding-approved.html</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">http://voyager.blogs.com/voyeurism/2011/11/the-six-learnings-project-extended-funding-approved.html</guid>
<description>in His perfect timing and all-sufficient Grace, God has provided for extended funding the Six Learnings Project. Extending the Six Learnings framework for curriculum design in Virtual Worlds (to give the project its full name) will be funded by a...</description>
<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>in His perfect timing and all-sufficient Grace, God has provided for extended funding the <a href="http://voyager.blogs.com/voyeurism/2009/08/the-starling-project---initial-funding-approved.html">Six Learnings</a> Project.</p>
<p><i>Extending the Six Learnings framework for curriculum design in Virtual Worlds</i> (to give the project its full name) will be funded by a grant worth approximately US$146,000, and is one of four approved-in-principle by the eduLab initiative between the Ministry of Education and the National Institute of Education.</p>
<p>if you are a principal of a school in Singapore and would like to know more, i would be happy to make an appointment with you to elaborate on the details :-)<br /></p>
<div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Voyeurism?a=5sUe9O1_cxE:SsA5niE8jSU:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Voyeurism?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Voyeurism?a=5sUe9O1_cxE:SsA5niE8jSU:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Voyeurism?i=5sUe9O1_cxE:SsA5niE8jSU:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Voyeurism?a=5sUe9O1_cxE:SsA5niE8jSU:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Voyeurism?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
