<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>as a follow-up to <a href="http://voyager.blogs.com/voyeurism/2011/10/i-have-been-invited-to-keynote-bedok-green-secondary-schools-teaching-learning-symposium.html">my earlier post</a>, the video is now ready :-)</p>
<p>once again, a sincere "thank you" to the Mdm Tay, Mr Lim and Mrs Loong, and the staff of Bedok Green Secondary School, for their warm hospitality and kind invitation :-)</p>
